214
00:13:53,860 --> 00:13:54,340
Sit.

215
00:14:00,060 --> 00:14:00,620
What's up?

216
00:14:00,780 --> 00:14:01,620
What is it?

217
00:14:07,020 --> 00:14:07,420
Xizhou,

218
00:14:08,740 --> 00:14:10,220
can we allocate

219
00:14:10,660 --> 00:14:12,460
some of the plants we found

220
00:14:12,580 --> 00:14:13,700
to the professor for research?

221
00:14:14,340 --> 00:14:15,620
He can use them to synthesize medicine

222
00:14:16,340 --> 00:14:17,900
to help the sick children.

223
00:14:18,740 --> 00:14:20,780
You mean the sick children

224
00:14:21,220 --> 00:14:22,580
in the village, right?

225
00:14:22,900 --> 00:14:23,860
You saw them?

226
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:25,540
I heard about them from Ruanruan.

227
00:14:26,100 --> 00:14:27,980
She went to take photos
of those children during the day.

228
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:31,340
Those kids...

229
00:14:31,460 --> 00:14:33,100
Grandpa and the board of directors
won't agree.

230
00:14:34,300 --> 00:14:35,860
I'll talk to Grandpa when I get back.

231
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:37,700
Just give me your support
when the time comes.

232
00:14:45,420 --> 00:14:46,020
Xizhou,

233
00:14:47,020 --> 00:14:48,020
you don't agree?

234
00:14:59,540 --> 00:15:00,140
Yunshen,

235
00:15:02,940 --> 00:15:04,660
I understand your desire to save lives.

236
00:15:06,020 --> 00:15:07,460
Those children are indeed unfortunate.

237
00:15:09,580 --> 00:15:10,820
Not only are they unfortunate,

238
00:15:12,660 --> 00:15:14,460
but they might also not even make it
to adulthood.

239
00:15:17,820 --> 00:15:18,900
Yunshen,

240
00:15:21,180 --> 00:15:21,700
you also know

241
00:15:21,820 --> 00:15:23,660
the company's current situation
isn't great.

242
00:15:25,180 --> 00:15:27,140
When you first proposed this project,

243
00:15:27,980 --> 00:15:29,940
Grandpa and I
wholeheartedly supported you.

244
00:15:30,140 --> 00:15:31,540
To provide you with sufficient funding,

245
00:15:32,340 --> 00:15:34,860
I didn't hesitate to cut the budget
for my department.

246
00:15:36,020 --> 00:15:37,340
Now, you're saying
you're not going to do it?

247
00:15:38,580 --> 00:15:39,060
You,

248
00:15:39,540 --> 00:15:39,980
me,

249
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:41,100
Grandpa,

250
00:15:41,300 --> 00:15:42,260
and even your mom

251
00:15:43,100 --> 00:15:44,580
will all be held accountable
by the board of directors.

252
00:15:46,940 --> 00:15:47,580
I know.

253
00:15:48,260 --> 00:15:50,020
That's why I suggested allocating some

254
00:15:50,940 --> 00:15:52,020
to Professor Hans.

255
00:15:52,540 --> 00:15:55,660
I'll also work hard
on developing my new project.

256
00:15:58,460 --> 00:15:59,860
You make it sound easy.

257
00:16:02,140 --> 00:16:03,220
Starting a new project

258
00:16:03,860 --> 00:16:05,420
isn't that simple.

259
00:16:06,260 --> 00:16:07,980
And the current project

260
00:16:08,620 --> 00:16:10,260
has significant commercial value.

261
00:16:11,220 --> 00:16:13,100
The company also needs some good news.

262
00:16:13,620 --> 00:16:14,260
Xizhou,

263
00:16:15,580 --> 00:16:16,660
you know

264
00:16:18,020 --> 00:16:19,740
I'm in pharmaceutical research
and development

265
00:16:20,340 --> 00:16:22,060
is to save lives.

266
00:16:29,420 --> 00:16:29,980
Yunshen,

267
00:16:30,980 --> 00:16:31,980
let me ask you this.

268
00:16:33,140 --> 00:16:35,060
How many children in that village
are sick

269
00:16:35,300 --> 00:16:36,220
in total?

270
00:16:36,420 --> 00:16:37,060
Five?

271
00:16:37,860 --> 00:16:38,460
Ten?

272
00:16:39,140 --> 00:16:40,100
Or twenty?

273
00:16:40,780 --> 00:16:42,460
Do you know
how many employees Lingtian has?

274
00:16:43,820 --> 00:16:44,660
Over five thousand.

275
00:16:53,900 --> 00:16:54,460
Xizhou,

276
00:16:56,500 --> 00:16:57,820
giving up some herbs

277
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:01,380
might slow down our progress.

278
00:17:01,900 --> 00:17:03,500
But it could give those kids

279
00:17:05,180 --> 00:17:06,540
a chance to survive.

280
00:17:06,940 --> 00:17:09,540
This project
is currently the company's hope.

281
00:17:10,980 --> 00:17:11,580
Yunshen,

