00:17:14,340 --> 00:17:15,820
still don't look good,

284
00:17:16,620 --> 00:17:18,700
the company will have to
undergo massive layoffs.

285
00:17:19,340 --> 00:17:20,820
The first to be let go

286
00:17:21,460 --> 00:17:23,100
will be the older employees.

287
00:17:24,140 --> 00:17:25,740
They have families to support.

288
00:17:26,180 --> 00:17:26,780
You're right.

289
00:17:27,700 --> 00:17:28,980
Illness is painful.

290
00:17:29,380 --> 00:17:33,020
But unemployment can push
many families into despair.

291
00:17:37,180 --> 00:17:37,700
Xizhou,

292
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:39,780
I get it now.

293
00:17:40,460 --> 00:17:41,300
I'll think it over.

294
00:17:52,660 --> 00:17:53,220
Xizhou,

295
00:17:54,540 --> 00:17:56,580
can you put off
the harvesting rights issue for now?

296
00:17:57,460 --> 00:17:58,660
I need more time to consider.

297
00:18:01,620 --> 00:18:02,100
All right.

298
00:18:02,780 --> 00:18:03,300
By the way,

299
00:18:03,500 --> 00:18:04,580
the helicopter is arriving tomorrow.

300
00:18:05,100 --> 00:18:06,220
We'll leave together then.

301
00:18:09,220 --> 00:18:10,140
About tomorrow,

302
00:18:11,420 --> 00:18:12,620
I won't go back for the time being.

303
00:18:14,540 --> 00:18:16,260
I'll stay and talk to Professor Hans

304
00:18:16,940 --> 00:18:19,740
to see if there are other options.

305
00:18:21,580 --> 00:18:22,220
All right, then.

306
00:18:22,860 --> 00:18:23,980
Take care of yourself.

307
00:18:25,380 --> 00:18:26,180
Get some rest.

308
00:18:44,260 --> 00:18:45,980
Don't wander around in this place.

309
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:48,380
If you need anything,
remember to find Yunshen.

310
00:18:52,700 --> 00:18:54,220
Although I'm reluctant to see you go,

311
00:18:54,740 --> 00:18:56,260
I'm a bit happy to see

312
00:18:56,620 --> 00:18:58,340
how worried you are about me.

313
00:19:00,620 --> 00:19:01,140
I'll get going, then.

314
00:19:03,700 --> 00:19:05,420
When you arrive, remember to call me
on the satellite phone.

315
00:19:05,540 --> 00:19:06,500
You must call.

316
00:19:07,100 --> 00:19:08,180
I'll miss you.

317
00:19:08,620 --> 00:19:10,020
You must miss me too.

318
00:19:10,620 --> 00:19:11,780
Three times a day.

319
00:19:19,780 --> 00:19:20,500
Don't forget.

320
00:19:20,860 --> 00:19:21,940
Come back
after you're done taking photos.

321
00:19:23,580 --> 00:19:24,340
I know.

322
00:19:26,700 --> 00:19:27,220
See you.

323
00:19:29,780 --> 00:19:30,500
Xizhou,

324
00:19:30,620 --> 00:19:31,860
safe journey!

325
00:19:51,900 --> 00:19:52,700
Dr. Zhu, Boss.

326
00:19:54,260 --> 00:19:55,020
This local freshly baked bread

327
00:19:55,140 --> 00:19:55,540
is delicious.

328
00:19:55,660 --> 00:19:57,340
Here, try some. Try some.

329
00:20:14,260 --> 00:20:15,300
Let me break off a piece for you.

330
00:20:15,740 --> 00:20:16,340
Hey, guys.

331
00:20:17,380 --> 00:20:18,740
We need to leave here right away.

332
00:20:20,220 --> 00:20:20,740
Did anything happen?

333
00:20:21,500 --> 00:20:22,540
Na Lu is unconscious.

334
00:20:22,980 --> 00:20:24,580
Several children have high fevers
that won't go down.

335
00:20:24,900 --> 00:20:27,300
I suspect it's a viral infection.

336
00:20:27,740 --> 00:20:28,540
What's the situation?

337
00:20:28,780 --> 00:20:29,500
I'm not sure yet.

338
00:20:29,900 --> 00:20:31,060
The medical conditions here are limited.

339
00:20:31,220 --> 00:20:33,020
I want to take these patients

340
00:20:33,300 --> 00:20:34,580
to Naotao Medical Station
as soon as possible.

341
00:20:34,820 --> 00:20:36,180
But those children are so young.

342
00:20:36,300 --> 00:20:37,980
Can they handle such a long journey?

343
00:20:38,100 --> 00:20:38,740
She's right.

344
00:20:39,100 --> 00:20:39,700
Professor,

345
00:20:40,420 --> 00:20:41,580
let's go by water.

346
00:20:41,700 --> 00:20:44,380
We'll ask Sen to find a boat now.

347
00:20:45,220 --> 00:20:47,100
All right. The faster, the better.

348
00:20:47,380 --> 00:20:48,060
All right.

349
00:20:48,620 --> 00:20:49,500
- Come on.
- Okay, let's go.

350
00:21:48,420 --> 00:21:50,300
All right, here we are.

351
00:21:51,140 --> 00:21:52,700
Be careful, everyone.

352
00:21:52,780 --> 00:21:54,540
One at a time.

353
00:21:54,580 --> 00:21:56,500
Madam, be careful.

354
00:21:57,860 --> 00:21:59,780
Watch your step.

355
00:22:00,660 --> 00:22:01,500
Be careful.

356
00:22:03,660 --> 00:22:04,500
One at a time.

357
00:22:04,660 --> 00:22:05,620
Give me the luggage.

358
00:22:35,580 --> 00:22:36,380
Professor Hans.

359
00:22:37,980 --> 00:22:38,660
Professor.

360
00:22:39,020 --> 00:22:39,660
How is it?

361
00:22:40,140 --> 00:22:41,460
The test results are in.

362
00:22:44,460 --> 00:22:45,740
They're infected

363
00:22:45,780 --> 00:22:47,020
with a virus called V-Four.

364
00:23:32,220 --> 00:23:32,620
Dr. Zhu.

365
00:23:32,740 --> 00:23:33,260
Le,

366
00:23:33,420 --> 00:23:34,540
why are you so early?

367
00:23:35,100 --> 00:23:36,300
I went to bed early, so here I am.

368
00:23:50,620 --> 00:23:53,300
My boss couldn't finish his breakfast

369
00:23:53,380 --> 00:23:54,300
and left some for you.

370
00:23:54,620 --> 00:23:55,460
Don't waste it.

371
00:23:55,540 --> 00:23:56,500
It's a shame to waste food.

372
00:23:56,780 --> 00:23:57,460
That's right.

373
00:23:57,740 --> 00:23:59,140
Boss spent all night on...

374
00:24:03,780 --> 00:24:04,180
Okay.

375
00:24:04,460 --> 00:24:05,420
I'll take them.

376
00:24:05,820 --> 00:24:07,700
Thank your Boss

377
00:24:08,020 --> 00:24:09,540
for his well-balanced

378
00:24:09,700 --> 00:24:10,620
leftover breakfast.

379
00:24:16,620 --> 00:24:17,100
Boss,

380
00:24:17,540 --> 00:24:18,740
Dr. Zhu says thank you.

381
00:24:19,620 --> 00:24:21,460
I think Dr. Zhu
isn't mad at you anymore.

382
00:24:21,700 --> 00:24:23,260
Look, she even finished the breakfast.

383
00:24:25,020 --> 00:24:27,780
No wonder they say
it's good to date a science guy.

384
00:24:28,180 --> 00:24:29,300
Boss, you're amazing.

385
00:24:29,580 --> 00:24:30,660
Enough talking. Let's go.

386
00:24:31,180 --> 00:24:31,540
Wait,

387
00:24:32,540 --> 00:24:33,060
where are we going?

388
00:24:33,060 --> 00:24:33,140
We're helping the villagers
with indoor disinfection.
where are we going?

389
00:24:33,140 --> 00:24:34,780
We're helping the villagers
with indoor disinfection.

390
00:24:34,860 --> 00:24:36,260
After that, we'll go up the mountain

391
00:24:36,300 --> 00:24:37,540
and see
if there are any usable medicinal herbs.

392
00:24:38,540 --> 00:24:39,580
We've only slept
for a little over two hours.

393
00:24:39,660 --> 00:24:40,260
Aren't we going back
to sleep a bit more?

394
00:24:40,380 --> 00:24:42,140
Didn't everyone only sleep
for about two hours?

395
00:24:43,900 --> 00:24:44,780
Are you talking about Dr. Zhu?

396
00:24:45,340 --> 00:24:46,380
I'm not sleepy. Are you sleepy?

397
00:24:47,220 --> 00:24:47,780
Yes.

398
00:24:48,780 --> 00:24:49,300
No, I'm not.

399
00:24:49,540 --> 00:24:50,260
So, am I sleepy or not?

400
00:24:50,300 --> 00:24:51,300
No, you're not.

401
00:24:51,620 --> 00:24:52,100
Wait.

402
00:24:52,380 --> 00:24:53,260
I'm not sleepy.

403
00:24:53,500 --> 00:24:54,700
But I'm just worried about you.

404
00:24:54,780 --> 00:24:56,940
Lack of sleep
can weaken your immune system.

405
00:24:57,020 --> 00:24:58,460
And then we might get infected
by the virus.

406
00:24:59,380 --> 00:25:00,100
No, you won't.

407
00:25:00,780 --> 00:25:02,780
You've been vaccinated
against every disease in the world.

408
00:25:04,180 --> 00:25:04,980
Boss,

409
00:25:05,540 --> 00:25:06,660
I can stay awake.

410
00:25:07,020 --> 00:25:08,340
Can you make me a sandwich

411
00:25:08,380 --> 00:25:09,940
to replenish my energy?

412
00:25:10,060 --> 00:25:11,220
Sure, I'll make one for you.

413
00:25:12,940 --> 00:25:13,500
Yes!

414
00:25:18,820 --> 00:25:22,140
(The V-Four virus spreads
through respiratory droplets.)

415
00:25:23,020 --> 00:25:26,020
(People with weakened immune systems
are more susceptible.)

416
00:25:27,580 --> 00:25:28,620
(After infection,)

417
00:25:28,860 --> 00:25:31,420
(the main symptoms
include respiratory issues,)

418
00:25:32,300 --> 00:25:33,180
(persistent high fever,)

419
00:25:33,660 --> 00:25:34,300
(coughing,)

420
00:25:34,540 --> 00:25:35,220
(shortness of breath,)

421
00:25:35,660 --> 00:25:36,580
(and difficulty breathing.)

422
00:25:37,380 --> 00:25:40,180
(Severe infections
can lead to pneumonia,)

423
00:25:40,740 --> 00:25:41,980
(acute respiratory distress syndrome,)

424
00:25:42,260 --> 00:25:43,180
(and liver and kidney failure.)

425
00:25:44,020 --> 00:25:45,860
(If not treated promptly,)

426
00:25:46,380 --> 00:25:47,420
(it can lead to death.)

427
00:25:48,540 --> 00:25:51,060
(So, those who have close contact
with the patients)

428
00:25:51,260 --> 00:25:52,500
(must be quarantined.)

429
00:25:53,100 --> 00:25:55,340
(Our medical station has limited beds.)

430
00:25:56,460 --> 00:25:57,900
(So we've set up
a temporary quarantine area.)

431
00:25:58,580 --> 00:26:00,180
(in the school classrooms.)

432
00:26:01,140 --> 00:26:04,020
(All students and parents
who have been in contact with Oscar)

433
00:26:04,420 --> 00:26:07,020
(will be quarantined here together.)

434
00:26:08,260 --> 00:26:09,500
(What we can do now)

435
00:26:11,100 --> 00:26:13,060
is to prevent the epidemic
from spreading further

436
00:26:14,380 --> 00:26:16,340
while waiting for the antiviral serum
to arrive.

437
00:26:17,100 --> 00:26:17,740
Guys,

438
00:26:18,660 --> 00:26:19,500
I'm counting on you.

439
00:26:49,940 --> 00:26:50,660
Danmin.

440
00:27:06,500 --> 00:27:07,850
[Hope]

441
00:27:07,950 --> 00:27:10,200
[Quarantine. No Entry]

442
00:27:23,780 --> 00:27:24,460
Miss,

443
00:27:25,660 --> 00:27:26,660
how's Danmin?

444
00:27:27,140 --> 00:27:28,060
Did I infect him?

445
00:27:28,140 --> 00:27:28,860
Don't worry.

446
00:27:29,340 --> 00:27:29,980
He's fine.

447
00:27:30,540 --> 00:27:31,580
You have to get better soon.

448
00:27:31,700 --> 00:27:33,060
So you can see him, okay?

449
00:27:34,740 --> 00:27:35,340
Okay.

450
00:27:36,060 --> 00:27:36,980
Have a good rest.

451
00:27:37,620 --> 00:27:38,340
Thank you.

452
00:27:54,860 --> 00:27:55,540
Uncle Hans,

453
00:27:55,700 --> 00:27:56,780
how's Danmin doing?

454
00:27:56,940 --> 00:27:58,380
Oscar is worried about him.

455
00:27:59,820 --> 00:28:01,220
Here is his test report for today.

456
00:28:03,220 --> 00:28:04,660
Danmin has shown

457
00:28:04,700 --> 00:28:05,980
some symptoms of V-Four.

458
00:28:06,420 --> 00:28:08,260
His white blood cell count is too low.

459
00:28:09,460 --> 00:28:12,220
At the time, Danmin cried
and wanted to go back to school.

460
00:28:12,300 --> 00:28:15,540
He said he missed his classmates
and teacher.

461
00:28:15,820 --> 00:28:17,300
I let them talk on the phone.

462
00:28:17,660 --> 00:28:18,860
But Danmin didn't cooperate.

463
00:28:19,020 --> 00:28:21,140
Oscar couldn't bear it.

464
00:28:21,260 --> 00:28:22,500
So he came to the hospital to see him.

465
00:28:23,660 --> 00:28:25,180
Even if it's not this virus,

466
00:28:25,820 --> 00:28:27,420
any bacteria in the air

467
00:28:27,460 --> 00:28:28,620
could take his life.

468
00:28:29,860 --> 00:28:30,500
But

469
00:28:30,780 --> 00:28:32,700
Danmin's mother and Anson understand

470
00:28:32,940 --> 00:28:34,020
and don't blame Oscar.

471
00:28:34,180 --> 00:28:35,980
After all, he's also seriously ill.

472
00:28:40,300 --> 00:28:40,900
Aunt Addy,

473
00:28:41,020 --> 00:28:42,140
why haven't we seen

474
00:28:42,220 --> 00:28:43,460
Oscar's family here?

475
00:28:43,940 --> 00:28:47,180
His wife recently went
to another village to teach.

476
00:28:47,340 --> 00:28:49,140
We've already informed her.

477
00:28:49,260 --> 00:28:49,820
Okay.

478
00:29:04,700 --> 00:29:05,220
Hello?

479
00:29:06,220 --> 00:29:07,100
Hello, Dr. Ji.

480
00:29:07,300 --> 00:29:08,620
How's the situation on your end?

481
00:29:09,900 --> 00:29:11,020
We've mostly identified those

482
00:29:11,140 --> 00:29:12,500
who have had contact with the patients.

483
00:29:12,780 --> 00:29:14,380
It's better than I expected.

484
00:29:14,460 --> 00:29:15,220
That's good.

485
00:29:16,260 --> 00:29:17,460
Hopefully,

486
00:29:18,740 --> 00:29:20,140
it would stop spreading.

487
00:29:23,660 --> 00:29:24,220
Mint,

488
00:29:24,860 --> 00:29:25,580
are you okay?

489
00:29:26,620 --> 00:29:27,580
I'm fine.

490
00:29:27,820 --> 00:29:29,740
It's just that the aid station
is a bit short-handed.

491
00:29:29,900 --> 00:29:31,220
So it's quite busy.

492
00:29:31,340 --> 00:29:32,820
Even if it's busy, you need to rest.

493
00:29:32,980 --> 00:29:35,100
Only by maintaining good health
can you work well,

494
00:29:35,260 --> 00:29:35,780
understand?

495
00:29:36,820 --> 00:29:37,420
Don't worry about me.

496
00:29:37,820 --> 00:29:39,020
Take care of yourself too.

497
00:29:39,420 --> 00:29:41,060
I'll leave the tribal area to you.

498
00:29:41,300 --> 00:29:41,780
Okay.

499
00:29:42,100 --> 00:29:43,220
Stay in touch.

500
00:30:53,140 --> 00:30:53,700
Thank you.

501
00:30:54,420 --> 00:30:55,340
You're welcome.

502
00:30:55,540 --> 00:30:56,380
Let's cooperate happily.

503
00:31:03,020 --> 00:31:03,740
What's wrong?

504
00:31:04,260 --> 00:31:09,580
The minister is asking about the progress
of the supply and medicine distribution.

505
00:31:10,100 --> 00:31:13,180
There's nothing that I can do
if the road is closed.

506
00:31:13,940 --> 00:31:15,860
There are nosy foreign journalists

507
00:31:15,980 --> 00:31:18,650
who want to go to
Naotao and Ninggu Village

508
00:31:18,650 --> 00:31:20,060
to report the epidemic.

509
00:31:20,980 --> 00:31:23,780
I have already released
the medicine and supplies.

510
00:31:24,220 --> 00:31:27,140
Aren't we waiting for the good weather
to fly?

511
00:31:27,220 --> 00:31:28,660
Tell the minister not to worry.

512
00:31:28,900 --> 00:31:32,820
They can't get into Naotao and Ninggu
without an airplane.

513
00:31:33,020 --> 00:31:34,860
We won't let them report it.

514
00:31:40,180 --> 00:31:41,420
What happened in Naotao?

515
00:31:42,260 --> 00:31:42,900
Nothing.

516
00:31:43,020 --> 00:31:44,340
Just a wild outbreak.

517
00:31:44,420 --> 00:31:45,660
That can be treated.

518
00:31:45,860 --> 00:31:47,660
We just have to send medicine.

519
00:31:48,460 --> 00:31:49,460
How long has it been?

520
00:31:49,900 --> 00:31:51,140
A couple of days.

521
00:31:53,340 --> 00:31:53,860
Sir,

522
00:31:55,100 --> 00:31:56,300
I need your help.

523
00:32:28,500 --> 00:32:29,220
Morning.

524
00:32:37,940 --> 00:32:39,100
What are you doing here?

525
00:32:39,420 --> 00:32:41,140
This medicine looks very familiar.

526
00:32:41,620 --> 00:32:43,500
There are many antiviral herbs here.

527
00:32:46,260 --> 00:32:48,460
What you're making looks
just like the traditional herbal pouch

528
00:32:48,540 --> 00:32:50,180
my grandmother used to make for me
when I was a child.

529
00:32:50,860 --> 00:32:53,060
Are you trying to use it
to treat V-Four?

530
00:32:53,900 --> 00:32:54,540
Just taking a shot.

531
00:32:54,620 --> 00:32:55,300
The roads are blocked,

532
00:32:55,380 --> 00:32:56,820
and even the helicopter can't get in.

533
00:32:56,980 --> 00:32:58,340
Waiting isn't an option.

534
00:33:03,060 --> 00:33:03,540
What are you looking at?

535
00:33:04,220 --> 00:33:04,940
Handsome, right?

536
00:33:05,820 --> 00:33:07,740
I usually look pretty handsome
when I'm working.

537
00:33:08,180 --> 00:33:09,220
Imagine me

538
00:33:09,300 --> 00:33:11,180
holding precision instruments.

539
00:33:11,780 --> 00:33:13,140
It's not something
ordinary people get to see.

540
00:33:14,380 --> 00:33:15,700
Yes, it's especially handsome.

541
00:33:16,420 --> 00:33:18,660
Your weather forecast
may not be accurate.

542
00:33:18,820 --> 00:33:20,740
But the herbal pouch
will definitely be useful.

543
00:33:21,460 --> 00:33:22,260
Dr. Zhu,

544
00:33:22,420 --> 00:33:23,220
Luca has a fever.

545
00:33:23,300 --> 00:33:24,380
Come and take a look quickly.

546
00:33:26,460 --> 00:33:27,500
Follow me to the examination room.

547
00:33:36,140 --> 00:33:36,860
Fu Yunshen.

548
00:33:37,700 --> 00:33:38,700
Xizhou said
you weren't answering the phone.

549
00:33:38,780 --> 00:33:40,020
You should call him back.

550
00:33:45,500 --> 00:33:46,740
Ruanruan, where's your camera?

551
00:33:47,660 --> 00:33:48,340
I'm not taking photos for now.

552
00:33:48,540 --> 00:33:49,820
They need extra hands here.

553
00:33:59,060 --> 00:33:59,500
Yes, Xizhou?

554
00:33:59,660 --> 00:34:00,740
There's an outbreak on your side.

555
00:34:00,820 --> 00:34:02,340
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

556
00:34:02,580 --> 00:34:04,700
I want you
to bring Ruanruan back with you now.

557
00:34:04,860 --> 00:34:05,620
You'll come back to Shanghai with me.

558
00:34:05,780 --> 00:34:07,420
It has been raining here

559
00:34:07,660 --> 00:34:08,420
and the roads are blocked.

560
00:34:08,580 --> 00:34:09,500
We can't get out.

561
00:34:09,740 --> 00:34:11,540
The weather is already improving.

562
00:34:11,580 --> 00:34:12,740
The government has sent a helicopter,

563
00:34:12,780 --> 00:34:14,260
medical teams, and serum.

564
00:34:14,340 --> 00:34:16,140
Both of you will fly back to the capital
on the helicopter.

565
00:34:16,380 --> 00:34:17,500
I can't, Xizhou.

566
00:34:18,060 --> 00:34:19,460
I need to work with the medical team

567
00:34:20,300 --> 00:34:21,620
and do some handover.

568
00:34:21,740 --> 00:34:23,020
Hand over what?

569
00:34:23,180 --> 00:34:24,380
You're not a doctor.

570
00:34:24,820 --> 00:34:26,060
Do you want me to go
with the medical team

571
00:34:26,140 --> 00:34:27,220
and drag you back here?

572
00:34:27,940 --> 00:34:28,460
Xizhou,

573
00:34:29,020 --> 00:34:30,620
don't exaggerate

574
00:34:30,740 --> 00:34:31,780
just because you heard
about the outbreak.

575
00:34:32,740 --> 00:34:35,700
We've already kept it under control.

576
00:34:36,260 --> 00:34:38,260
The infected villagers
have all been isolated.

577
00:34:38,340 --> 00:34:39,060
So I'm fine. Don't worry about me.

578
00:34:39,140 --> 00:34:40,460
With the serum,
there won't be any more problems.

579
00:34:40,580 --> 00:34:41,180
So don't worry anymore.

580
00:34:42,060 --> 00:34:44,060
Yunshen, can you listen to me once?

581
00:34:44,380 --> 00:34:45,820
Just for once!

582
00:34:46,980 --> 00:34:47,540
Hello?

583
00:34:47,980 --> 00:34:49,700
Xizhou, the signal is bad.

584
00:34:50,220 --> 00:34:51,140
By the way,

585
00:34:51,340 --> 00:34:53,180
I entrust you
Grandpa and Madam Jiang's matters.

586
00:34:53,300 --> 00:34:54,300
Keep this a secret and you know why.

587
00:34:54,820 --> 00:34:55,420
Hello?

588
00:34:55,860 --> 00:34:56,820
Fu Yunshen lied to you.

589
00:34:56,900 --> 00:34:57,940
The signal is good here.

590
00:34:58,660 --> 00:34:59,220
Ruanruan,

591
00:34:59,500 --> 00:35:00,580
the medical team here

592
00:35:00,900 --> 00:35:02,300
might go over at any time.

593
00:35:02,620 --> 00:35:04,020
If Yunshen doesn't come back,

594
00:35:05,060 --> 00:35:06,020
you should come back first.

595
00:35:06,620 --> 00:35:08,100
I'm staying too.

596
00:35:08,420 --> 00:35:09,860
Why are you causing trouble too?

597
00:35:10,700 --> 00:35:11,660
Gosh, I'm not.

598
00:35:11,820 --> 00:35:13,820
Before coming here,
Zhizhi prepared various medicines for me.

599
00:35:13,940 --> 00:35:14,780
So don't worry.

600
00:35:15,660 --> 00:35:16,820
I haven't married you yet.

601
00:35:17,100 --> 00:35:18,540
How can I die just like that?

602
00:35:21,020 --> 00:35:23,900
Are you really worried about me
right now?

603
00:35:24,060 --> 00:35:25,540
Then you better keep worrying about me.

604
00:35:26,100 --> 00:35:27,340
I want to enjoy

605
00:35:27,420 --> 00:35:29,100
this special treatment longer.

606
00:35:32,060 --> 00:35:32,740
Hello?

607
00:35:34,860 --> 00:35:35,500
Hello?

608
00:35:37,020 --> 00:35:38,300
I guess the signal is really bad here.

609
00:35:39,100 --> 00:35:39,740
What are you doing?

610
00:35:39,980 --> 00:35:42,060
You've never seen the cutest person
in the universe?

611
00:35:42,380 --> 00:35:44,780
If Fu Xizhou dares not to marry you,

612
00:35:45,100 --> 00:35:46,900
I'll sever ties with him.

613
00:35:49,820 --> 00:35:50,380
Righteous man.

614
00:35:51,420 --> 00:35:51,980
Just being wise.

615
00:35:52,660 --> 00:35:53,140
I'll get going.

616
00:35:53,980 --> 00:35:54,500
Bye-bye.

617
00:35:54,700 --> 00:35:55,580
Be safe.

618
00:36:11,020 --> 00:36:11,620
Dr. Zhu,

619
00:36:12,420 --> 00:36:13,340
where's Professor Hans?

620
00:36:14,340 --> 00:36:15,180
He's busy inside.

621
00:36:15,260 --> 00:36:16,100
Are you looking for him?

622
00:36:17,380 --> 00:36:18,180
- This is...
- Dr. Zhu,

623
00:36:18,380 --> 00:36:19,740
I'm Oscar's wife.

624
00:36:19,900 --> 00:36:21,140
Is my husband okay now?

625
00:36:21,340 --> 00:36:22,300
I'd like to see him.

626
00:36:22,500 --> 00:36:23,420
He has an infectious disease.

627
00:36:23,460 --> 00:36:24,820
You can't see him now.

628
00:36:25,380 --> 00:36:26,340
I'll be careful.

629
00:36:26,500 --> 00:36:27,980
I will wear protective gear.

630
00:36:28,260 --> 00:36:29,780
Can I just take a quick look?

631
00:36:29,820 --> 00:36:30,660
Please!

632
00:36:30,740 --> 00:36:31,460
Mint,

633
00:36:31,860 --> 00:36:33,180
Oscar is experiencing
a hyperactive immune response.

634
00:36:33,300 --> 00:36:34,060
The conditions here

635
00:36:34,140 --> 00:36:35,740
make it difficult
to provide further treatment.

636
00:36:35,820 --> 00:36:36,740
What do you mean?

637
00:36:37,260 --> 00:36:38,340
What happened to my husband?

638
00:36:38,460 --> 00:36:39,060
This won't do.

639
00:36:39,180 --> 00:36:39,820
I have to see him.

640
00:36:39,860 --> 00:36:40,780
I must see him now!

641
00:36:40,820 --> 00:36:41,860
If you go and see him,

642
00:36:41,900 --> 00:36:42,900
you could easily get infected.

643
00:36:43,060 --> 00:36:43,940
It's too dangerous.

644
00:36:44,020 --> 00:36:45,180
Please.

645
00:36:45,260 --> 00:36:46,300
I'm not afraid to die.

646
00:36:46,460 --> 00:36:47,780
I can sign an agreement.

647
00:36:47,860 --> 00:36:49,580
My decision has nothing to do with you.

648
00:36:49,660 --> 00:36:50,500
Please take her away.

649
00:36:50,620 --> 00:36:51,500
This is the quarantine area.

650
00:36:51,700 --> 00:36:52,580
It's too dangerous.

651
00:36:52,780 --> 00:36:53,700
Get her out of here quickly.

652
00:36:56,020 --> 00:36:56,580
Ms. Xu, come.

653
00:36:58,220 --> 00:36:59,220
Please take care of her.

654
00:37:02,180 --> 00:37:03,420
What happened to my husband?

655
00:37:04,420 --> 00:37:04,980
Ms. Xu,

656
00:37:05,260 --> 00:37:06,180
go home first.

657
00:37:06,780 --> 00:37:08,860
The doctors said
they would take good care of them.

658
00:37:10,540 --> 00:37:12,220
When can I see him?

659
00:37:13,340 --> 00:37:14,500
I believe it will be soon.

660
00:37:16,460 --> 00:37:17,380
Uncle Hans!

661
00:37:20,980 --> 00:37:21,900
Uncle Hans.

662
00:37:22,620 --> 00:37:23,300
If...

663
00:37:23,740 --> 00:37:24,660
I mean

664
00:37:24,780 --> 00:37:26,460
if there is any possibility
that I could help her take precautions

665
00:37:26,540 --> 00:37:27,580
so they can meet for a moment?

666
00:37:27,740 --> 00:37:30,020
We don't have any antiviral serum
right now.

667
00:37:30,340 --> 00:37:31,820
We can't let her take that risk.

668
00:37:31,980 --> 00:37:32,820
I understand.

669
00:37:33,020 --> 00:37:34,380
But if we watch her

670
00:37:34,940 --> 00:37:36,340
and don't let them
have any close contact,

671
00:37:36,420 --> 00:37:37,500
just let them meet once.

672
00:37:37,620 --> 00:37:38,820
Or perhaps say a few words,

673
00:37:38,980 --> 00:37:40,580
- Oscar's condition might...
- Mint.

674
00:37:41,260 --> 00:37:42,500
You're a doctor.

675
00:37:42,860 --> 00:37:44,700
You must be responsible for every life.

676
00:37:45,300 --> 00:37:46,780
You can't let your emotions
get the best of you.

677
00:37:52,860 --> 00:37:54,460
Yes, I know.

678
00:37:55,460 --> 00:37:56,820
Have you ever thought about it?

679
00:37:59,580 --> 00:38:01,460
If Oscar were to die like this,

680
00:38:02,460 --> 00:38:04,580
they might not even have a chance
to say goodbye.

681
00:38:05,140 --> 00:38:05,740
Mint,

682
00:38:06,860 --> 00:38:08,460
I'm disappointed in you.

683
00:38:20,620 --> 00:38:22,900
- I must see him today!
- You can't go inside!

684
00:38:23,140 --> 00:38:25,140
If I don't see him now,
it will be too late.

685
00:38:25,180 --> 00:38:26,700
This is the quarantine area.

686
00:38:26,980 --> 00:38:29,140
- You can't!
- I must see him!

687
00:38:29,300 --> 00:38:29,980
Xu Li!

688
00:38:30,300 --> 00:38:31,500
Calm down!

689
00:38:31,980 --> 00:38:33,420
Didn't we agree beforehand?

690
00:38:33,540 --> 00:38:35,380
If you don't let me see him now,

691
00:38:35,540 --> 00:38:36,380
can you guarantee he'll be able

692
00:38:36,420 --> 00:38:37,980
to stand in front of me
without harm after this?

693
00:38:38,060 --> 00:38:39,340
We'll take good care of him.

694
00:38:40,340 --> 00:38:42,500
I can't leave like this, Dr. Zhu.

695
00:38:43,820 --> 00:38:45,060
I have to go inside now.

696
00:38:45,580 --> 00:38:46,780
I have something to say to him.

697
00:38:50,900 --> 00:38:53,180
We had an argument

698
00:38:54,140 --> 00:38:55,660
before we left previously.

699
00:38:56,980 --> 00:38:58,780
I said a lot of things I shouldn't have

700
00:39:01,220 --> 00:39:02,900
and hurtful things.

701
00:39:03,580 --> 00:39:05,100
He must be feeling terrible

702
00:39:05,180 --> 00:39:06,700
all alone in there right now.

703
00:39:09,060 --> 00:39:11,140
I have to go in and be with him

704
00:39:11,340 --> 00:39:12,180
to tell him

705
00:39:12,780 --> 00:39:13,780
that I miss him

706
00:39:13,940 --> 00:39:14,980
and I love him.

707
00:39:17,500 --> 00:39:19,100
We've been together
from university until now,

708
00:39:19,900 --> 00:39:21,540
for most of our lives.

709
00:39:23,740 --> 00:39:26,460
I can't let
the last thing he heard from me

710
00:39:27,140 --> 00:39:28,380
was I hate him.

711
00:39:41,020 --> 00:39:41,540
Hello?

712
00:39:42,100 --> 00:39:43,140
Hi, Dr. Hans.

713
00:39:43,420 --> 00:39:44,340
Tomorrow morning,

714
00:39:44,460 --> 00:39:46,860
the medical team
will fly the serum over.

715
00:39:47,580 --> 00:39:48,580
That's great.

716
00:39:49,180 --> 00:39:50,740
That is good news.

717
00:39:52,180 --> 00:39:54,140
So you guys hang on

718
00:39:54,260 --> 00:39:56,100
and wait for us, okay?

719
00:39:56,380 --> 00:39:56,940
Okay.

720
00:39:57,420 --> 00:39:59,180
Thank you. Thank you.

721
00:40:18,900 --> 00:40:21,220
[Hope]

722
00:40:47,980 --> 00:40:48,580
Honey,

723
00:40:49,380 --> 00:40:50,220
are you okay?

724
00:40:52,140 --> 00:40:52,860
I'm okay.

725
00:40:55,780 --> 00:40:56,460
I'm sorry

726
00:40:56,660 --> 00:40:57,740
to have left you alone.

727
00:40:57,940 --> 00:40:59,060
How did you get in?

728
00:41:00,460 --> 00:41:02,220
Aren't you afraid I will infect you?

729
00:41:02,780 --> 00:41:03,740
That would be great.

730
00:41:04,900 --> 00:41:06,420
Then I can lay next to you.

731
00:41:09,940 --> 00:41:11,180
This is great.

732
00:41:12,220 --> 00:41:13,500
I was just wishing

733
00:41:13,780 --> 00:41:17,020
that I hope I can see you
when I open my eyes.

734
00:41:17,340 --> 00:41:19,020
If I can see you one last time,

735
00:41:22,300 --> 00:41:23,620
I can die happily.

736
00:41:23,860 --> 00:41:26,260
No, you can't, Oscar.

737
00:41:28,060 --> 00:41:30,060
I can't live without you.

738
00:41:31,580 --> 00:41:32,620
Don't say that.

739
00:41:35,620 --> 00:41:37,460
You will be sad in the beginning.

740
00:41:38,500 --> 00:41:39,900
Don't stay here alone.

741
00:41:42,220 --> 00:41:43,460
You have to go back home

742
00:41:43,580 --> 00:41:48,020
and let your family and friends
to keep you company.

743
00:41:48,700 --> 00:41:50,020
Eat good food,

744
00:41:51,860 --> 00:41:52,580
travel,

745
00:41:52,660 --> 00:41:53,860
and do things

746
00:41:55,460 --> 00:41:59,700
that you have always wanted to do.

747
00:42:06,420 --> 00:42:08,780
But don't forget me too soon.

748
00:42:11,100 --> 00:42:13,220
Remember me for a few years

749
00:42:14,980 --> 00:42:16,900
before you change to a handsome guy.

750
00:42:20,100 --> 00:42:20,980
I love you.

751
00:42:22,460 --> 00:42:23,860
I will always love you.

752
00:43:13,180 --> 00:43:16,780
♪I see you in a dark corner♪

753
00:43:17,060 --> 00:43:20,420
♪With vulnerability overwhelming you♪

754
00:43:20,660 --> 00:43:22,740
♪Biting your lips
and facing away from me♪

755
00:43:22,980 --> 00:43:26,980
♪You break the walls of stubbornness♪

756
00:43:27,820 --> 00:43:30,780
♪Once more, another sundown
swiftly passes by♪

757
00:43:31,060 --> 00:43:36,220
♪Love is like a lie at the end
of the century♪

758
00:43:36,380 --> 00:43:42,140
♪That almost fools me♪

759
00:43:52,020 --> 00:43:58,620
♪A kiss can heal this wrecked world♪

760
00:43:58,940 --> 00:44:05,580
♪If there is a slight possibility
of avoiding loneliness♪

761
00:44:05,860 --> 00:44:12,260
♪Let me endure the heavy rainfall
with you♪

762
00:44:12,540 --> 00:44:16,580
♪If there is a slight possibility♪

763
00:44:16,820 --> 00:44:22,700
♪The moon that once shone for me
should stay radiate♪

764
00:44:23,020 --> 00:44:28,820
♪You'll regain happiness
when you are true to yourself♪

765
00:44:38,300 --> 00:44:45,260
♪You feel my pain♪

766
00:44:45,380 --> 00:44:52,340
♪No reason for those meaningless winds
to pass by me♪

767
00:44:52,580 --> 00:44:59,260
♪When the meaningless things hit me♪

768
00:45:07,140 --> 00:45:13,620
♪Why must we miss out on each other
when our hearts are broken?♪

769
00:45:14,300 --> 00:45:20,900
♪Imitating others who flinch and escape
after love sparks fade away♪

770
00:45:21,060 --> 00:45:29,900
♪All I yearn for
is the warmth deep within you♪
